---
import { Image } from "@astrojs/image/components";
import kulkaImg from "../images/temp-picture.jpg";
---

<section class="flex items-center text-slate-50">
	<div class="mx-4 lg:ml-0 space-y-8">
		<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold">About me:</h2>
		<div class="flex gap-4 items-center">
			<div class="h-16 w-16 rounded-full relative">
				<Image
					src={kulkaImg}
					alt="Krzysztof Kulka"
					class="h-full aspect-square object-contain rounded-full"
				/>
			</div>
			<div>
				<h3 class="text-xl">Hi! I'm <strong>Krzysztof Kulka</strong></h3>
				<p>Based in Poland (Płock).</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="max-w-md space-y-4">
			<h4 class="text-lg font-semibold">
				Switch from digital marketer to frontend developer
			</h4>
			<p>
				After +10 years as a digital marketer / manager / head of marketing, in
				2021 I felt in love with AI & ML apps, such as:
			</p>
			<ul class="list-disc ml-8">
				<li>
					<a
						href="https://madgicx.com/"
						target="_blank"
						rel="nofollow"
						class="underline">Madgix</a
					> (ads automation & optimization)
				</li>
				<li>
					<a
						href="https://jasper.ai/"
						target="_blank"
						rel="nofollow"
						class="underline">Jasper</a
					> (content creation with GPT)
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p>I didn’t want to miss that train. One year later, I started coding.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
